# Python Backend

- Keep FastAPI routes thin; put workflows in `src/khukra/application/` or `src/khukra/services/`.
- Keep DuckDB access in repositories under `src/khukra/data/repositories/`.
- Register domain behavior through existing registries instead of ad hoc imports.
- Add pytest coverage for changed domain, API, repository, or service behavior.
- Run `ruff check src tests` and `pytest tests -q` for backend changes.
- Preserve public response shapes unless the PR documents a breaking change.
